::Prowl::

"Computer, locate unit Iron Raptor," Prowl says as he exits his quarters, 
reluctantly setting off toward the location where the computer had reported 
to him (War Room). He was going to find Iron Raptor, and then he was going to 
apologize.

After thinking it over in his quarters, he decided that it was best to just 
say sorry. He couldn't bear not being able to touch his love, and if 
apologizing would solve the problem, he'd just have to swallow his pride.

He rounds a corner in time to see Iron Raptor touching Hot Rod on the arm, a 
wave of jealousy washing over him. He narrows his eyes, walking up to Iron 
Raptor.

"Hello, love," he says, glancing from her to Hot Rod.
